Classes in net.sourceforge.metrics.calculators that implement ICalculator
 class AbstractLinesOfCode
          Replace old LOC calculator which does not handle comments correctly.
 class Calculator
          Abstract base class for all metrics calculators.
 class InheritanceDepth
          Calculates Depth of Inheritance Tree, Number of Children and sets superclasses to either 0 or 1 (if the source has subclasses)
 class LackOfCohesion
          Calculates the Lack of Cohesion of Methods (LCOM*) metric using the Henderson-Sellers method (See book page 147): (avg(m(a)) - m)/(1 - m) where m(a) is the number of methods that access a.
 class LinesOfCode
          Deprecated. Use AbstractLinesOfCode instead (and MethodLinesOfCode / TotalLinesOfCode)
 class McCabe
          Calculate McCabe Cyclomatic Complexity for a method.
 class MethodLinesOfCode
          Calculates MLOC: Method Lines of Code
 class NestedBlockDepth
          Calculate max nested block depth for a method
 class Norm
          Calculates number of overridden methods for a class.
 class NumberOfAttributes
          Counts the number of attributes in a class.
 class NumberOfMethods
          Counts the number of methods in a class.
 class NumberOfParameters
          Counts the number of parameters for a method
 class RMartinCouplings
          Calculates the Robert Martin Coupling metrics (Ca, Ce, I, A and Dn);
 class SpecializationIndex
          Calculates the SI (NORM * DIT) / NOM.
 class TotalLinesOfCode
          Calculates TLOC: Total Lines of Code
